74
00:05:11,911 --> 00:05:13,246
{\an8}He takes such good care of us.

75
00:05:13,313 --> 00:05:14,347
{\an8}GENTA MATSUDA

76
00:05:14,414 --> 00:05:16,249
{\an8}-He's our big bro.
-That's right.

77
00:05:18,217 --> 00:05:20,853
<i>The younger members treat him
like their big brother.</i>

78
00:05:23,690 --> 00:05:26,826
{\an8}<i>Toshiya Miyata
is always the life of the party.</i>

79
00:05:27,794 --> 00:05:31,097
{\an8}<i>He is both cheerful
and considerate of others.</i>

80
