{\an8}<i>We follow the seven members
as they embark on separate journeys.</i>

86
00:05:54,487 --> 00:05:59,258
{\an8}Ready? And, action!

87
00:06:00,927 --> 00:06:04,630
<i>It's December 2019,
and Tamamori is filming a drama.</i>

88
00:06:06,399 --> 00:06:08,768
